namespace Agriculture

features
	Agriculture {abstract}
		mandatory
			CropType {abstract}
				alternative
					Grain {abstract}
						alternative
							Wheat
							Rice
					Vegetable
			Fertilizer {abstract}
				or
					Organic
					Chemical
		optional
			IrrigationSystem {abstract}
				alternative
					Drip
					Sprinkler
			PestControl {abstract}
				or
					Biological
					Pesticide
constraints
	Rice => IrrigationSystem
	Organic => !Pesticide
	Pesticide => Chemical